Usage: reset_clock_groups [-help] {-physically_exclusive  | -logically_exclusive  | -asynchronous } {-name <name_list> | -all }

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-all                     # Removes all physically exclusive, logically
                         # exclusive, or asynchronous clock groups in the
                         # design (bool, optional)
-asynchronous            # Asynchronous clock groups to be removed
                         # (bool, optional)
-logically_exclusive     # Logically exclusive clock groups to be removed
                         # (bool, optional)
-name <name_list>        # Previously defined names of clock groups to be
                         # removed (string, optional)
-physically_exclusive    # All physically exclusive clock groups to be removed
                         # (bool, optional)